{
  "stem": "19550.6",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 232.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the, the Germans would-- that, that sole German officer and the gendarmerie would present themselves to the council.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they would tell the council that on such and such date there will be a evacuation, and you have to tell the population that they should prepare themselves for in such and such a way.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they would put up placards in key spots in a-- in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] the fact that they, that they told you that you can take food and clothing along or that you should was sufficient to calm your worst fears.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this is the kind of simple elementary psychology that the Germans practiced all over, in the concentration camps, everyplace.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It isn't the gullibility of human beings.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It is, rather, the desperate need of human beings to cling to, to life and to cling to the positive, the hopeful which was exploited so-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I'm sure that at certain levels, it was very conscious and very planful on the part of the Germans, but you really didn't have to be conscious and planful about it.",
      "word_count": 61
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "If you were a German SS man and you were told from higher ups that you announced that there was going to be a evacuation and the, and the evacuees will be allowed to take 50 kilograms each of clothing and--",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, [SIGHS] I, I know a few things that I was very particular about.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One was I had a pair of boots, very heavy [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] mountain-climbing boots from my days in, in Switzerland.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was very sure to take that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you know, we all tried to get-- mind you, this was going into the summer.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
